Cell["\<\
As another example, consider the code space of the phase-flip correction \
code. It is spanned by the following two logical basis states.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->2089082548,ExpressionUUID->"9e74ca34-cfaa-4d2a-aa46-f578f6e88dca"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"ss", "=", 
   RowBox[{"S", "[", 
