Cell["\<\
One can convince oneself that these logical Pauli operators commute with all \
the generators (and hence all elements) of the stabilizer.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1072145489,ExpressionUUID->"fcbbdfbf-5bc1-4d03-abaa-33083a8d993d"],

