Cell["\<\
The initial stage marked by the vertical dashed line is just to share an \
entangled pair, and we start the analysis from this point. Then, the \
generators of the stabilizer are given by\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1891391469,ExpressionUUID->"cadc50df-5252-4def-afac-1858c8b068f4"],

